<section class="py-10">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Frequently asked</h2>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-3">
    <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-100 border border-base-300">
      <input type="checkbox">
      <div class="collapse-title font-medium">What's included in the $500?</div>
      <div class="collapse-content text-base-content/70 text-sm">
        A perpetual license to run <%= Docuseal.product_name %> on your own infrastructure, with unlimited users, unlimited documents, and all features (API, webhooks, DOCX pipeline, audit trail, branding, OTP 2FA). You also get 12 months of updates from purchase.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-100 border border-base-300">
      <input type="checkbox">
      <div class="collapse-title font-medium">What happens after year 1?</div>
      <div class="collapse-content text-base-content/70 text-sm">
        Your license never expires — you can keep using the version you have forever. To continue receiving updates after the first year, you can renew update support at a reduced rate.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-100 border border-base-300">
      <input type="checkbox">
      <div class="collapse-title font-medium">Are there any per-user or per-envelope fees?</div>
      <div class="collapse-content text-base-content/70 text-sm">
        No. Add as many users and send as many documents as your hardware supports. Your cost is fixed regardless of volume.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-100 border border-base-300">
      <input type="checkbox">
      <div class="collapse-title font-medium">Where is my data stored?</div>
      <div class="collapse-content text-base-content/70 text-sm">
        On your own servers, your own database, and your own object storage. Nothing goes to a vendor cloud unless you explicitly configure it. This is ideal for regulated industries (finance, healthcare, legal, government).
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-base-100 border border-base-300">
      <input type="checkbox">
      <div class="collapse-title font-medium">Can I migrate away later?</div>
      <div class="collapse-content text-base-content/70 text-sm">
        Yes. All signed PDFs, audit trail PDFs, and submission data live in standard formats on your storage. There's no lock-in.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-12">
  <div class="card-hero shadow-xl">
    <div class="card-body items-center text-center py-12 px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3">Buy once. Use forever.</h2>
      <p class="text-white/80 text-lg max-w-xl mb-6">Skip the per-seat treadmill. Self-host, own your data, and pay $500.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-3">
        <%= link_to 'Get started', new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-accent btn-lg px-10 shadow-glow' %>
        <%= link_to 'See use cases', use_cases_path, class: 'btn btn-ghost btn-lg text-white' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
